Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Field Magic, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temple of the Royal Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid... Seems you've gotten your "Trap Hell" started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the card that shall deliver onto you God's punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have already activated the Trap Card this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Monster Card!\N Embodiment of Apophis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He Summoned three Monsters at {\i1}once{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Inherited Card:\N Psycho Shocker Counterattacks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap Monster Summon...?\N Was that what Malik was aiming for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Effect of Jounouchi-kun's Monster Box disappears this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Malik attacks with all three next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of Jounouchi's Monsters will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Is there anything that can save my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Jounouchi can somehow set a counter card before he ends his turn, he may have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got ahead of myself\N and went on the attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}... only to fall straight into another one of his traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then switch Wyvern Warrior\N to Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that meant to help you somehow avoid my attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This will do the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My card is Scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if all three Apophis attack me at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}three of the four will take the hits and I'll make it through this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had best prepare yourself, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avatars of Apophis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-way attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys'll block your\N Trap Monsters' attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can avoid direct damage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Trap!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Jammer, activate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Jammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding one card from your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can negate the activation of your opponent's Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a legendary rare card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then the goats...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scapegoat is wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Apophis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyvern!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one target left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Direct Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he just barely made it out alive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your strategy,\N you cannot defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of Jounouchi's Monsters are dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and he only has 200 Life Points left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you do nothing, he will have no choice but to place his hand on his deck
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and surrender to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This fool's {\b0}lower{\b1} than a lab rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a lab {\b0}fly{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just can't win...\N He's way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik's strong even without using dirty tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have nothing else up my sleeves...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}, my brother really can't win anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, I told you this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling is a world of cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's your sibling fighting, you can't turn your eyes away from this reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the very least, he can fight on until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's... nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! I have something to tell you before you surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A winning Duelist has to take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lost to you...\N Insector Haga, Esper Roba, and Ryota Kajiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was them fighting here in your place, what do you think they would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lost to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would they think if they saw you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, maybe you shouldn't care about those who lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you inherit the loser's dreams along with your win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fate of someone who wants to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is what makes a {\i1}real{\i0} Duelist who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind shaming them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,place your hand on the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For yourself and for your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for {\i1}me{\i0} as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have you by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have been to scared to have my surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to take off the bandages either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't you you, big brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would still be wandering in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've continued to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you gave me the light I needed to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gave you light...\N while you wandered in darkness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back then, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You poor thing! If we leave him all alone, this child will surely die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I met the Ishtar family,\N I was given the light to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Jounouchi gave light to his sister...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see you give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, will you answer one question for me before the end arrives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you seek by fighting in this Battle City tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I must fight no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep my {\i1}promise{\i0} with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've met all kinds of people on my journey to this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I fought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I followed my path while fighting against them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it! That's my Battle City!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I got something to say to {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back that "before the end" crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If I lose here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what am I gonna tell the guys I fought who paved the path for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of them fought me 'till the very end without giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Mai, Shizuka and Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is nothing more you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is having the courage to accept their loss not also a part of being a Duelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What can you see, but can't see?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have a close to zero hope of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just give up that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what a real Duelist is, the thing I'm aiming to become!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll struggle down the path I've chosen with the deck I built!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Let's settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! My fight has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you still have the guts to press forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set two reverse cards on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Swordsman of Landstar in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it a Trap or a Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there is no way he can stop all three of the Apophis' attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he only has 200 of his Life remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my prey so desires it,\N I shall destroy you in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Avatars of Apophis!\N Eliminate the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, open!\N Foolish Burial!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets you\N choose a card from your deck
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and place it in the opponent's Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also open my other set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on robbing my Temple of the Royal Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call the Monster I placed in your Graveyard back to the field with Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I call back to the field is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!\N Psycho Shocker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! You Summoned a 7-Star Monster in a little-to-no time at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And due to Psycho Shocker's Special Ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all Trap Cards on the field are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recall that you Summoned those Apophis guys with a Trap Card earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll activate\N Psycho Shocker's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Crush!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a card I won from someone I fought against, containing his very {\i1}soul{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!\N You turned the tables!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally found a way to counter Malik's Trap Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} what're ya gonna do?\N Your strategy won't work on me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Psycho Shocker...\N So he had that in his deck all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's poison for\N that Trap Deck of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He turned the situation around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I hadn't won this card from Roba,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've gotten stronger thanks to the guys I fought who got me this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the near-dead cat got back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Struggle more for me, my lab rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me see the third God Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Kung-Foo Fighter Ultimator!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I switch Swordsman of Landstar into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyber Energy Shock!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My attack ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Kung-Foo Fighter Ultimator and Swordsman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it! Now Malik's Life Points were greatly reduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just needs one more attack to finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost there, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's payback for your three attacks from those Apophis freaks earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an impressive comeback, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being almost out of Life Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you showed your pride as a Duelist by standing up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this guy really the same Malik we've been fighting all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget how you brainwashed me and forced me to fight my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! I'm gonna kick your ass no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid, I can't believe you let {\b0}Jounouchi{\b1} push you this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't disappoint me too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need you to win this tournament as my double.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no need to worry, Lord Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have already prepared what I need to dispose of Psycho Shocker in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Swords of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Swords of Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now none of Jounouchi's Monsters can move for three turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He almost had him beat, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using Magic Cards to make up for his Trap Cards' flaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if his Monsters can't move for three turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as he has the Psycho Shocker's abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik can't use his Trap Strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} should still have the advantage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't attack, I can still keep Summoning Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Kung-Foo Fighter Ultimator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Legendary Fisherman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kajiki, I'm using your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch my other Monsters on the field to Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-this card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like you finally drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our "Special Card" that should be placed in the sacred alter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is this in my deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Temple of the Royal Family is the card I've used to pose as Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The actual card needed to be placed in that alter should not be in my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I placed that card in your deck just before the Duel began.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you can play the role of Malik even more {\b0}realistically{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Malik!\N Hurry up and play your damn card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I set a card face-down on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I doubt he'd play a Trap Card with Psycho Shocker's Ability in play...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means... it's a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good! Place that card in the sacred alter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as it is within the sacred alter of Temple of the Royal Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it can't be touched by the enemy's attacks or their Magic effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Lord Malik, if the temple should fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...if that card should lose, the player will automatically lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fret not, Rishid!\N That card is {\b0}invincible{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since he drew that card from his deck this turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's been acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something really bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That ark in the temple's alter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you noticed it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That temple is meant to protect something and keep out intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ark must hold some kind of secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he hasn't\N revealed what that secret is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is your turn over yet or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have not declared its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seal one card away within the ark in the temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sealed a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So there really was a secret...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What card did he just put in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It {\b0}couldn't{\b1} be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the Magic Card Resurrection of the Dead this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive, Wyvern Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then sacrifice Wyvern Warrior and Swordsman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! Insect Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haga! This is the card you gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lend me your strength, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That valuable card sure is wasted on a mere lab rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among all of Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those are some of the most valuable cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Jounouchi-kun's deck has really powered up from the Battle City tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then! The Effects of Sealing Swords of Light disappear on my next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have a single Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're history if I attack you with all three of my Monsters at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you will not be touching me with {\i1}any{\i0} of those Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as the card I placed in the ark remains within the Temple of the Royal Family's alter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it shall not be harmed by the enemy's attacks or magic effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was simply using the Sealing Swords of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a way to buy time while I prepared for a {\i1}ritual{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the time has now come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three cards I've gathered on the field
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hold the power to Summon the great guardian of the temple, protecting the sacred sealed card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian of the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Cup of Sealed Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I open my reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal of Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Temple of the Royal Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I gather these three Magic Cards together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Summon the Mystical Beast, who protects the secrets of the alter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystical Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The guardian of the temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scorpion God that shall {\i1}devour{\i0} your Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show your glorious form before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Mystical Beast, Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?! What the hell just came out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\N Another monster just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mystical Beast Selket exists to guard the sacred card sealed in the ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacred card?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, the card you sealed in that ark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's the God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,137)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card he won via the Ante Rule helped Jounouch escape countless pinches,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what the heck is that grotesque Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After attacking Jounouchi's Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it ate them from head to toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Selket absorbs the Attack Points of the Monsters it eats,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,increasing its Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Ra Card is sealed in the ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
